Deg [[Tanzeggit|tenzeggit]], '''Tigni''' neɣ '''Tizwi''' d [[akat]] n tuẓẓma n twinest neɣ n tuzza. Ma d tigni n kra n [[itrikli|umtiweg]] iga d [[Azunglay|tizzungeltis]]. [[Tuzza]] tla (tesɛa) tigni n 0, ma d [[tagra (tusnakt)|tagra]] timifedg usdid ila tigni n 1.

Amtiweg [[Tallit n tuzzya|amazzay]] ila amili agaman i wemsel neɣ i tigni,[[tadusi n webralmas|Asemdu n webralmas]] isselfaw-d '''tamerruzt tasbegsant'''.<br/>
S tusnak, tigni tettwafek-d s: 

::<math>f=\mbox{ver}(o\!\varepsilon)=2\sin^2\left(\frac{o\!\varepsilon}{2}\right)=1-\cos(o\!\varepsilon)=\frac{a-b}{a}\approx\frac{15\pi}{4GT^{2}\rho}\ ;</math>
anda <math>a</math> d <math>b</math> gan d izenzaren n [[Aggad|waggad]] d [[tiglezt taraklant|usafaylu]] n umtiweg, s umdafar, d <math>o\!\varepsilon\,\!</math> iga d ’'''aɣwali uɣmir'''. Tamawaẓt d taɣbelt deg tegʷnit n umtiweg amengi seg [[tineẓẓi|tneẓẓi]] tayiwnit, dɣa tga d tasɣent n [[imezgi aldayan|imezgi aldayan aseddayan]], <math>G</math>, n [[tallit n tuzzya]] <math>T</math> yakk n tneẓẓi <math>\rho</math>.<br>
Akken i tella daɣen tigni tis snat, ''f' '' (tikwal tettwasezmel « ''n'' ») :

::<math>f'=\tan^2\left(\frac{o\!\varepsilon}{2}\right)=\frac{1-\cos(o\!\varepsilon)}{1+\cos(o\!\varepsilon)}=\frac{a-b}{a+b}</math>.

